### Subscription API
@host = http://localhost:3001
@token = REPLACE_WITH_ACCESS_TOKEN

### 4 plan жагсаалт (public)
GET {{host}}/api/subscription/plans

### Миний subscription
GET {{host}}/api/subscription/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Plan-ыг шууд идэвхжүүлэх (DEV / TEST)
POST {{host}}/api/subscription/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "planType": "COMBO",
  "period":   "monthly"
}

### Захиалга цуцлах (BASIC руу буцаах)
POST {{host}}/api/subscription/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Контент үзэх эрх шалгах — Live TV
POST {{host}}/api/subscription/access
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "kind": "live-tv"
}

### Контент үзэх эрх шалгах — Premium VOD
POST {{host}}/api/subscription/access
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "kind": "library",
  "vodId": "vod_test_id"
}
